src:
Na Obali eksplodiral bankomat
Zlikovci so bili spet dejavni.
06 Nov 2019, 07:03 by A. L.
ŠKOFIJE – Danes malo po 4. uri je bila policija obveščena, da so v Škofijah razstrelili bankomat. To so nam potrdili pri PU Koper. Pobrali so denar, več pa sledi v kratkem.
text:
An ATM exploded on the coast
The villains were active again.
06 Nov 2019, 07:03 by A.L.
BISHOP - Shortly after 4 a.m., police were informed that an ATM had been blown up in Bishops. This was confirmed to us at PU Koper. They picked up the money, and more follow shortly.
